    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system that provides seamless torque across the powerband up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag six-speed manual gearbox is paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through corners. This chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original suspension geometry with no bushing deflection. The engine bay is concours-clean, showing no signs of thermal fatigue or fluid seepage. A meticulously documented service history confirms that all critical maintenance intervals, including valve adjustments, have been strictly adhered to.",
